subproject.description: UNDP support to the Civil Service Reform Programme (CSRP) is intended to support the efforts being made by the Government of Ethiopia to build a fair, responsible, efficient, effective and transparent civil service by focusing on institutionalization of the Leadership Development Programme.
subproject.title: Civil Service Reform Programme
